Vietnam_Cashew_Association ( VINACAS ) would like to welcome you to the Golden_Cashew_Rendezvous_Vietnam 2015 including a number of the most important events of Vietnam cashew industry in 2015 : the International_Cashew_Convention_Vietnam & Cashew_Exhibition 2015 - VINACAS Silver_Jubilee :
1 . Time : 3 days , from 22nd to 24th of November 2015 .
2 . Venue : In_Ho_Chi_Minh city , Vietnam :
- Independence_Palace_Saigon . Address : 108 Nguyen_Du , Ben_Thanh_Ward , Ho_Chi_Minh city ( the International_Cashew_Convention_Vietnam 2015 ) .
- Rex_Hotel_Saigon . Address : 141 Nguyen_Hue_Street , District 1 , Ho_Chi_Minh city ( the Silver_Jubilee ) .
- Cashew exhibition place : Tanimex-LA , Tan_An city , Long_An province ( 40 kms from Ho_Chi_Minh city ) .
The event ' s will be updated at the website : http : / / events.vinacas.com.vn /
